Package smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper

Class ActuatorDataModelMapper

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper.ActuatorDataModelMapper
@Component public class ActuatorDataModelMapper extends Object
This class is responsible for mapping actuator data models (database entities) to actuator domain objects (core business logic entities). It utilizes an ActuatorFactory for creating domain objects from ActuatorMap which is a detailed, structured representation of actuator data. An ActuatorMapper is used for intermediate transformations between ActuatorDTO and ActuatorMap.
